name: Todolist
tagline: To Do List Project on Java EE Course , Lecturer : Haim Michael
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.

At This Website you can Register as a new user and Create and Manage you're personal To Do List.
you can create a To Do List item , Edit a To Do List Item , 
you can also use the check box feature for Multiple Completing of Item's  

### Authors and Contributors
The ToDOList Project was created by Amir Granot @DCAG and Oz Dagmi @dagmioz
